<lb n="0082a28"/><note place="inline">十五</note></p>
<lb n="0082a29"/><p>世尊復告曼殊室利。<note n="0082013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如是〕－【甲】</note><app n="0082013"><lem>如是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>如來一百八名號
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0936.0082b" n="0082b"/>
<lb n="0082b01"/><note n="0082014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝若【甲】</note><app n="0082014"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>自<note n="0082015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晝＝書【甲】</note><app n="0082015"><lem>晝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">書</rdg></app>。或使人書為經卷受持讀誦。如壽
<lb n="0082b02"/>命盡復滿百年壽。終此身後得往生無量福
<lb n="0082b03"/>智世界無量壽淨土。陀羅尼曰。</p>
