<lb n="0084a09"/><p>若有方所自書<note n="0084002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寫〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0084002"><lem>寫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。使人書<app type="＊" source="0084002"><lem>寫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>是無量壽經
<lb n="0084a10"/>典之處。則為是塔皆應恭敬作禮。若是畜生。
<lb n="0084a11"/>或<note n="0084003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝為【甲】</note><app n="0084003"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>鳥獸得<note n="0084004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞〕－【甲】</note><app n="0084004"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是經。如是等類。皆當不久
<lb n="0084a12"/>得成<note n="0084005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一切〕－【甲】</note><app n="0084005"><lem>一切</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>種智。陀羅尼曰。</p>
