<lb n="0084b03"/><p>若有能供養是經者。則是供養一切諸經等
<lb n="0084b04"/>無有<note n="0084006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（別）＋異【甲】</note><app n="0084006"><lem>異</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">別異</rdg></app>。陀羅尼曰。</p>
