<lb n="0084b08"/>底<note place="inline">十</note>伽迦娜<note place="inline">十一</note>莎訶某<app type="＊" source="0082012"><lem>持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">特</rdg></app>迦底<note place="inline">十二</note>薩婆婆
