<lb n="0084b29"/><p>如<note n="0084007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝是【甲】</note><app n="0084007"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>大海水可知滴數。是無量壽經典所生
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0936.0084c" n="0084c"/>
<lb n="0084c01"/>果報。不可數量。陀羅尼曰。</p>
