<lb n="0084c07"/><p>若有自<note n="0084008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書＋（寫）【甲】</note><app n="0084008"><lem>書</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">書寫</rdg></app>。使人書寫。是無量壽經<note n="0084009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔典〕－【甲】</note><app n="0084009"><lem>典</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。又能
<lb n="0084c08"/>護持供養。即如恭敬供養。一切十方佛土如
<lb n="0084c09"/>來無有別異。陀羅尼曰。</p>
